  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SocketTimeoutException
    This is a platform independent class used to represent network timeout exceptions, taking the place of java.net.SocketTimeoutException in JSimple based code.
    UnknownHostException
    This is a platform independent class used to represent I/O exceptions, taking the place of java.io.IOException in JSimple based code.
